<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">我问你<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay8 />
你有遇到过什么可怕的事，
<anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />让你吓到脸色铁青吗？</message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">可怕的事？<10_4 />
<anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我想想<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />夜里散步的时候，<delay8 />
遇见在黑暗中疯狂舞蹈的
<tag a="110" b="11" arg="0xcd00" /><anim id="TakenAback" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" />的瞬间吧！
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />据说在室外练习<delay8 />更容易集中精神，<delay20 />
这算是他独特的<delay8 />
身心统一方式吧。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="0" />原来如此，<delay20 />
那确实挺吓人的啊。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="004" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">可怕的事？<10_4 />
<anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我想想<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />之前<tag a="110" b="11" arg="0xcd00" /><delay8 />
在看一本叫
“豁出命来<tag a="135" b="6" arg="0xcd00" />”的书<anim id="Shocked" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Confused" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我超担心<delay8 />
那家伙是不是在想什么<delay8 />
鲁莽的事情！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="005" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">可怕的事？<10_4 />
<anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我想想<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />前阵子，<delay8 />
我没关门就外出了<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay8 /><anim id="OhGeez" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />什么东西都没丢哦！<pageBreak />但是，<delay8 /><tag a="135" b="7" arg="0xcd00" />上
残留着咬过的痕迹。<delay20 /><anim id="TakenAback" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" />
<anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />可我完全不记得自己有吃过啊。</message>
	<message label="101" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那么<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay8 />
该用什么来决一胜负呢<tag a="110" b="0" /><tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="102" attrib="00 00 03 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />嗯——<delay8 />我想想<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay40 />
<anim id="Aha" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><20_3 arg="8" />啊、<delay8 /><20_3 arg="6" /><tag a="110" b="3" />！<20_2 arg="4" /><delay frames="40" />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你来得正好！<pageBreak /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我正和<delay8 /><tag a="110" b="31" arg="0xcd00" />讨论，<delay8 />
要比试什么来决出最强的男人<delay20 />
才最合适！<pageBreak /><anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="3" />，
你觉得什么好啊？</message>
	<message label="102_a" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">掰手腕</message>
	<message label="102_b" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">接龙</message>
	<message label="102_c" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">唱歌</message>
	<message label="103" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Shocked" target="actor" targetSpec="" />掰手腕吗！<delay20 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><20_2 arg="5" />是我擅长的比试呢！<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />每日不懈锻炼，
<anim id="SmugFace" target="actor" targetSpec="" />终于练成了这肌肉！<delay40 />
我可不会轻易输给你哦！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="104" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">嘿，<delay8 /><anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你可别太小看我啊？<delay20 /><20_2 arg="7" />
我对自己的腕力<delay8 />
<anim id="SmugFace" target="actor" targetSpec="" />还挺有自信的呢！</message>
	<message label="105" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />接龙吗！<delay20 />
<20_2 arg="5" />普通的接龙有点无趣，<delay8 />
来玩“肌肉接龙”<anim id="TakenAback" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /><delay8 />怎么样？！<pageBreak /><anim id="Worried" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /><anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />只用肌肉的部位来接龙，
以此决一胜负！<delay20 />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />这接龙也充满了力量吧？！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="106" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Silent" target="actor" targetSpec="" />开什么玩笑！<delay40 />
<20_2 arg="7" />按那种规则，<delay8 />这接龙还怎么玩啊！<pageBreak />腹肌<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
肱二头肌<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
<anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />接个两三句就接不下去啦！</message>
	<message label="107" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Shocked" target="actor" targetSpec="" />唱歌吗！<delay20 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />唱歌的基本功就是腹式呼吸！<delay20 />
<20_2 arg="5" />先气沉丹田<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><tag a="10" b="12" /><anim id="Cheering" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><delay20 /><10_10 /><size value="150" />肱二头肌～♪<anim id="Worried" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /><size value="100" /></message>
	<message label="108" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Silent" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我耳膜都要被震破啦<tag a="110" b="0" /><20_2 arg="7" /><anim id="ShyBoy" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" />
<anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />唱歌可不是声音越大越好啊！</message>
	<message label="201" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />听好咯，<delay8 /><tag a="110" b="31" arg="0xcd01" />！<delay20 />
要想成为一个强悍的男人，<delay8 />
<anim id="Negative" target="actor" targetSpec="" />光是力气大还远远不够啊。<pageBreak /><anim id="Silent" target="actor" targetSpec="" />首先你得学会<delay8 />
用存在感制造压力。<delay20 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />能学会这招<delay8 />才算是真正的男子汉！<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="202" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="TakenAback" target="actor" targetSpec="" />只用存在感<delay8 />制造压力？！<10_4 />
<anim id="Frantic" target="actor" targetSpec="" />这种东西要怎么锻炼，<delay8 />
我可是<delay8 />完全摸不着头脑啊？！</message>
	<message label="203" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />别担心，<delay8 />这很简单。<delay20 />
就算有人瞪着你也千万别慌了手脚，<delay8 />
<anim id="Silent" target="actor" targetSpec="" />记住要时刻保持堂堂正正的姿态！<pageBreak /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />还有就是你的语调。<delay20 />
和对方说话的时候，<delay8 />
一定要干脆利落、<delay8 />声音宏亮！<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="204" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />原来如此，<delay20 />
确实能从<tag a="110" b="31" arg="0xcd00" />身上<delay8 />
感受到一些很强大的东西呢！<pageBreak /><anim id="IdeaBulb" target="actor" targetSpec="" />对了！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="31" arg="0xcd00" />的那个口头禅，<delay8 />
我也可以模仿吗？<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />用了“<tag a="110" b="5" />”，<delay8 />感觉就能更接近
<anim id="SmugFace" target="actor" targetSpec="" />有毅力的<delay8 />男人了呢！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="205" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />好啊！<delay20 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你就尽管拿去用吧！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
